<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>284</hymn_number>
<title>O, Táńirim, jer betinde РӘЖ284</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 O, Táńirim, jer betinde,
 Esimiń qandaı qasıetti esim.
 O, Táńir, dáripteımiz esimińdi, atyńdy Iem.
 Seni madaqtaımyz, beıbit ómir Ámirshisi,
 Uly Qudaı, Uly Táńir.</lyrics>
</song>